short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: WUT MISSION IS TO REPLACE ‘WHAT’ IN OXFORD DICTIONARY

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing WUT IT! Our innovative plugin that seamlessly transforms every occurrence of the word "What" into "Wut" across all pages, enhancing your browsing experience. 

Embark on a transformative journey with us as we advocate for the evolution of language by striving to redefine "What" to "Wut" within the esteemed Oxford dictionary. Join the ranks of WUTTERs and stay connected with us on Twitter as we pioneer this linguistic shift!
